tweet: Thankfully, the boyfriend never even came. I talked to New Girl & we eventually were friendly through high school.   I saw her a few years ago when I was working at Family Video & she didn’t even seem to remember me.   Me, the guy who once punched her face. 🤷🏻‍♂️  THE END.

name: Jordan Campbell
tweet: So now not only have I accidentally punched the New Girl, but now one of my friends is about to get his ass beat because of it.   My day has become something out of a Seinfeld episode.  So now I was in a predicament & a thought came to my head I’m not proud of. (8/?)

name: Jordan Campbell
tweet: I tell him I’ll talk to New Girl.   He says “You BETTER! Because this isn’t even the worst of it!”  I’m like “Huh?”  He says “People overheard New Girl talking to her boyfriend on her cell phone and she told him to come to our school during lunch time to kick MY ass!”  (7/?)

name: Jordan Campbell
tweet: Reeves says “She told the principal she got punched & she pointed out ME as the one who punched her! I was sent to the office & tried to explain that I wasn’t the one who punched her!”  “WHAT?!”  He says “Principal made me say sorry and the New Girl thinks I was lying!” (6/?)

name: Jordan Campbell
tweet: I go to my morning classes and it’s all I can think about: I punched the New Girl.   After 3rd Period ends my friend Reeves runs up to me in hallway & says “DUDE! WTF!”.  I say “I know I know I feel horrible for her.”  He says “For her?! Feel bad for ME!”  I’m like “Huh?”  (5/?)

name: Jordan Campbell
tweet: I go “I am so so so SO SORRY! Oh my god! Are you okay?! I didn’t mean to punch you I swear!”  I reach out to console her & she says “NO! Just get away from me!” and she runs away.  I feel miserable. I’ve went from being a pacifist my whole life to punching the New Girl...(4/?)

name: Jordan Campbell
tweet: AND BAM! SHE WALKS RIGHT INTO MY PUNCH!  Now, let me be clear, I have a very weak arm. To me, it felt like a baby fist brushed her cheek.   So I’m thinking “Fuck fuck fuck surely she’s good that couldn’t have hurt.”  Tears fill her eyes and she says “Are you kidding me?!”...(3/?)

name: Jordan Campbell
tweet: As I usually do with my stories, I was being super extra. I was recreating the specific moves and shit I executed in my dream to defeat my foes.   As I was showing off my super punch, a girl who had switched schools and was having her VERY FIRST DAY AT OUR SCHOOL walks by...(2/?)
